  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5258051">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5258051/" class="title-link">大二时 慢慢读完的</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5258051"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/43122006/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u43122006-10.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/43122006/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">跑偏君</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-01-06"
      class="main-meta">2012-01-06 20:35:55</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5258051_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  读完花了一个暑假。。 记得大二时暑假，每天起床之后坐到地上翻一翻，然后再去吃早餐，然后去学画。 别人问我讲什么的，我说：“就是通识读本，讲了很多东西，具体的不记得了。” 喜欢这种读书的状态：没有目的性的去记忆，忘了具体的内容，就是感觉读完后心境变了。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5258051/#comments">(5回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 1没用</span>
